Colombia to Buy Back Up to 39.5 Trillion Pesos of Securities

-- B y   A n d r e a   J a r a m i l l o   a n d   H e l e n   M u r p h y
-- 
2011-09-09T22:17:44Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-09/colombia-to-buy-back-up-to-39-5-trillion-pesos-of-securities-1-.html
Colombia  will buy back up to 39.5
trillion pesos ($22 billion) worth of local debt due between
2012 and 2014 as it seeks to issue new securities maturing in
August 2026.  Colombia will seek to repurchase peso bonds due April 2012,
August 2012, April 2013, November 2013 and May 2014, and offer
in return peso debt due October 2015, October 2018 and August
2026, the  Finance Ministry said  in a statement today. The swap
will be carried out Sept. 20, according to the statement.  To contact the reporters on this story:
Andrea Jaramillo in Bogota at 
